org.apache.poi.ddf

Class EscherSpgrRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherRecord
      • org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherSpgrRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public class EscherSpgrRecord
extends EscherRecord
    The spgr record defines information about a shape group. Groups in escher are simply another form of shape that you can't physically see.(spGR记录定义有关形状组的信息。埃舍尔中的群体只是另一种你无法亲眼看到的形状形式。)
